{"tid":1298170,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"元朗大馬路搞「反天價橋遊行」","createTime":"2019-07-08T20:11:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-09T10:08:39.000Z","uid":75250,"like":14,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"01f58a5403203bbd22c438f989b80da5a8f08d50","tid":1298170,"uid":75250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T20:11:19.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">有冇得諗？</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n會唔會有朗屏站宏樂街集合，跟住沿着明渠出發去到大馬路，然後到元朗站終點？<br />\n<br />\n(Wiki)... 工程造價估計達<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">17億</span></strong>港元，將成為全香港每米造價最昂貴的行人天橋，且遠離繁忙之大棠路、靠近現有元朗廣場行人天橋，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">使用量預計將會不及現有行人天橋</span></strong>，惹來非議。<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">五大建築測量專業學會罕有聯手反對</span></strong>，並提出替代方案。<br />\n<br />\n... 2019年2月22日，政府無視社會反對意見，路政署決定為工程進行招標，同時聘請奧雅納為負責設計及監督有關建造工程的顧問公司，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">預計工程在2019年7月展開</span></strong>。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://zh.m.wikipedia.org/zh-hk/元朗行人天橋系統\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.m.wikipedia.org%2Fzh-hk%2F%E5%85%83%E6%9C%97%E8%A1%8C%E4%BA%BA%E5%A4%A9%E6%A9%8B%E7%B3%BB%E7%B5%B1&d=Xf5vvBv8GY7fsWMyNBE0dsg1Od0Dt6CGL4wHSLmh2%2Bg%3D&h=c07b03ab\" target=\"_blank\">https://zh.m.wikipedia.org/zh-hk/元朗行人天橋系統</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hyd.gov.hk/tc/road_and_railway/road_projects/6182tb/index.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hyd.gov.hk%2Ftc%2Froad_and_railway%2Froad_projects%2F6182tb%2Findex.html&d=Xf5vvBv8GY7fsWMyNBE0dsg1Od0Dt6CGL4wHSLmh2%2Bg%3D&h=a20fc9c6\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hyd.gov.hk/tc/road_and_railway/road_projects/6182tb/index.html</a>"},{"pid":"3252f0d8a2b506574679db52df13878cb8484a40","tid":1298170,"uid":75250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T20:29:55.000Z","msg":"終點改去鄉議局情願有冇得諗？<br />\n十八鄉鄉事委員會<br />\n元朗<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://goo.gl/maps/kYbUN59h9F3NCxtt8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2Fmaps%2FkYbUN59h9F3NCxtt8&d=Xf5vvBv8GY7fsWMyNBE0dsg1Od0Dt6CGL4wHSLmh2%2Bg%3D&h=3d3bc941\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://goo.gl/maps/kYbUN59h9F3NCxtt8</a>"},{"pid":"2c6e425edd1d892c12d06df74f1bdf42141cc39d","tid":1298170,"uid":75250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T20:44:52.000Z","msg":"拋磚引玉 俾啲意見<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1009ffee98df206e06ffeb688920ec83044d5872","tid":1298170,"uid":232065,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T20:49:24.000Z","msg":"兩刃劍<br />\n本地居民唔介意貴，因為唔係佢比<br />\n反對可能冇左條橋，居民未必like 。<br />\n<br />\n其他區既支持者去到，未必受歡迎<br />\n<br />\n去到唔反對起橋，其他人又未必滿意"},{"pid":"4527be6dcfa259e4f2261f3dcc08f40417ba599c","tid":1298170,"uid":67553,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T20:50:27.000Z","msg":"唔係唔好，但係怕依家搞遊行會搶咗五大訴求嘅焦點，令其他反送中遊行少咗人出，同埋畀人覺得我哋呢一班人借機爆晒啲不滿出嚟，唔係想爭取啲咩"},{"pid":"78e7af7eea36ce781d4b997e559e5b2c1a2f1471","tid":1298170,"uid":75250,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"4527be6dcfa259e4f2261f3dcc08f40417ba599c","tid":1298170,"uid":67553,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T20:50:27.000Z","msg":"唔係唔好，但係怕依家搞遊行會搶咗五大訴求嘅焦點，令其他反送中遊行少咗人出，同埋畀人覺得我哋呢一班人借機爆晒啲不滿出嚟，唔係想爭取啲咩"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T20:57:58.000Z","msg":"同意，呢啲比較side quest。<br />\n應該攞返正個Focus"},{"pid":"a302d2c3fb68bea9d0850cb32bfb3d41b5e5b016","tid":1298170,"uid":127447,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3252f0d8a2b506574679db52df13878cb8484a40","tid":1298170,"uid":75250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T20:29:55.000Z","msg":"終點改去鄉議局情願有冇得諗？<br />\n十八鄉鄉事委員會<br />\n元朗<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://goo.gl/maps/kYbUN59h9F3NCxtt8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2Fmaps%2FkYbUN59h9F3NCxtt8&d=Xf5vvBv8GY7fsWMyNBE0dsg1Od0Dt6CGL4wHSLmh2%2Bg%3D&h=3d3bc941\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://goo.g